name: Navy Braided Top
description:
This navy knit top hosts three rows of fabric braids around the neckline. Fabric is soft and lightweight (62% polyester, 30% rayon, 8% spandex). Looks great with your favorite jeans or a great skirt!

[Care Instructions]
Machine wash cold, delicate cycle, line dry.

[Fit]
This top is fitted but not tight and the hem hits at the hip. Please refer to size chart for further information.

name: Navy Braided Dress
description:
This navy knit dress hosts three rows of fabric braids around the neckline. Fabric is soft and lightweight (62% polyester, 30% rayon, 8% spandex).

[Care Instructions]
Machine wash cold, delicate cycle, line dry.

[Fit]
This dress is fitted but not tight. Our model is wearing a size 4 with the hem hitting 16 & 1/2 inches below her waist.
Please refer to size chart for further information.

[Styling Ideas]
Try it with a belt and your favorite heels or sandals! Tights and a blazer or jean jacket would be a great accompaniment in the cold months :)
